The paper deals with computer vision and machine learning techniques to model visual compatibility between objects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of deep learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) another likely category. The proposed method involves discovering patterns, which is a common theme in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another possible category. The paper also deals with a large dataset, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
